Lydia


Company Sector: Mobile Apps, Software, Fintech
Headquarters: Paris, France

Founded Date: 2013-01-01
# of Employees: 247
Website: https://lydia-app.com/
Description: Lydia develops a mobile payment platform intended to make payments easier. Lydia is a social interface that connects phones with cards to pay anyone with one app, allowing users to make pain-free payments through a mobile wallet system without carrying any cheques or ATM card.
Total Amount Raised to Date: $73.8M
